        icthyology, global change biology, statistical modeling, and eDNA metabarcoding analysis. 
    </p>
    <p>
        I want to understand how organisms are able to adapt to their environments as well as the factors which
        gave rise to the immense biodiversity seen across the tree of life. I'm interested in elucidating the
        genetic basis of evolutionary mechanisms such as speciation and selection, both across ecological and evolutionary
        timescales. 
    </p>
